Kabhi Khushboo,Kabhi Jhonkaa,Kabhi Havaa Saa LageKoi Dastak,Koi Aahat,Koi Aavaaz Nahin
Tu Dabe Paanv Khyaalon Mein Chalaa Aataa Hai
Baarhaa Aisaa Bhi Mahsoos Huaa Hai Mujhko
Aake Chupchaap Tu Pahloo Mein Baith Jaataa Hai
Tu Kahin Aaj Bhi Mujh Mein Zindaa Zindaa Saa Lage
Judaa Hokar Bhi Tu Mujhse Judaa Judaa Saa Lage
Kabhi Khushboo,Kabhi Jhonkaa,Kabhi Havaa Saa LageAaj Bhi Lams Dhadakte Hain Mere Seene Me.N
Aaj Bhi Teri Khanakti Si Sadaa Aati Hai
Aaj Bhi Jism Sulagtaa Hai,Teri Saanson Se
Aaj Bhi Rooh Mein Halchal Mere Mach Jaati Hai
Dil Teri Yaad Se Ab Yun Bharaa Bharaa Saa Lage
